====== H8548: תָּמִיד ======

===== Source =====

from an unused root meaning to  ;

===== Meaning =====

stretch properly,  continuance  (as indefinite  extension ); but used only (attributively as adjective)  constant  (or adverbially,  constantly ); elliptically the  regular  (daily) sacrifice

===== Definitions =====

  - stretch
  - continuance
  - extension
  - constant
  - constantly
  - regular

===== Usage =====

alway(-s), continual (employment, -ly), daily, (n-)ever(-more), perpetual.
